Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the hellish Tea Party,\NBig Mom finally shrieked.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And her past has been revealed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin destroyed the village of Elbaph!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother Carmel saved Linlin who was on a rampage...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Carmel had a different, secret side.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trafficking kids for 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the greatest product we've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And on Linlin's birthday, it happened.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We piled up your favorite sweet, Semla,\Nand made this Croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Launcher Blasts!\NThe Moment of Big Mom's Assassination!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}63 years ago, Mother Carmel and the other children\Nwent missing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were two people who witnessed the whole thing\Nwhich even Big Mom herself didn't know.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One of them was a warrior from Elbaph,\Nwho came down to see if the House of Lambs was okay.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He turned pale and started running,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and never came back to this island again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eventually, all the Giants in Elbaph\Nand the other places got to know the story{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:06:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Charlotte Linlin has been even more hated\Nby the Giants...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to the extent that\Nno one wants to utter her name.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?! Mother! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the other witness...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was a cook who used to be a pirate\Nand was living on the island she was left on, named Streusen.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was amused by it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He had an ability...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to turn any object into food,\Nwhich was the Cook-Cook Fruit power.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a monster like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I let her be alone, she'd die.\NThat's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just keep crying,\Nyou'll only get hungrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, little girl,\Ndo you wanna talk about your dreams or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't come too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man, have you seen Mother?\NDon't you know where everyone's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...\NBut I bet they'll come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll stay with you until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at cooking.\NIf it's just you, I can provide enough food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These two who met at the time\Nwill be the co-founders of the Big Mom Pirates.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses! They'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, at the tea party today,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if we break that picture in half,\Nwhat do you think will happen?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mama would be devastated!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And no one there would be able to move\Nfor more than five seconds!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then the KX Launcher will show\Nits real strength...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the Emperor of the Sea - Big Mom -\Nwill die!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doomed, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:10:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone gets in my way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True happiness for people is to be equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to find a country like that in the world today\Nis nearly impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's make this place our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A country where everyone will look at things\Nin the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a country without racism or\Nanything of that sort
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone will look at things\Nin the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the same way! That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone should get bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a beautiful dream, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's work hard together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me too!\N--Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this place a dreamland!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best too, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good girl, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are a lot of countries like that,\Nthe world will be more peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone can become happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother's dream was my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace? Is that your dream, Linlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is! I'll build a country\Nthat Mother would like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop crying already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey! I wanna see Mother's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was good at doing magic tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she put out her hands like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flower, flower! Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The magic trick that Mother used to do!\NWhy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flower, flower! Flower, flower! Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Earth!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Earth!\N--Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...\NIs that a Devil Fruit power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Flower, flower! Flower, flower!\N--Tree! Tree!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flower, flower! Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:13:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flower! Flower, flower! Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I could do it too, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she returns,\NI'm gonna show it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Tree!\N--Flower! Flower, flower! Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What an amazing power!\NShe's the real deal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Linlin!\NLet's sing together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How interesting! Alright, I decided!\NI'm gonna set out to sea with her!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nice! Nice!\N--A country where...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...everyone grows big\Nand looks at things in the same way and is equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Linlin. Let's build the dreamland!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The appointed time is long past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she didn't run away with the kids!\NThat damn Carmel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she did such a thing,\Nshe'll be in trouble with Cipher Pol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard a voice from somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--{\i1}Flower, flower!{\i}\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flower, flower! Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flower, flower! Flower, flower! Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flower, flower! Flower, flower! Flower, flower!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers are singing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tree, tree, tree!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's play, let's play!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's play, let's play!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's play!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's play, let's play!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on with this forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's play, let's play!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You're Charlotte Linlin, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Now, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all bad people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It hurts! So sad! It really hurts!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? The flowers say, "It hurts"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!\NDon't think she's just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eventually, the two took to sea\Nand showed what they were capable of,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and became infamous.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at this wanted poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 50 million berry bounty for a kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A castle fell at the hands of a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mastermind is Charlotte Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cipher Pol reported that she's a security risk!\NShe'll become a powerful villain one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch her at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tarte tropezienne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouglof au chocolat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madeleine! Brioche!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the colorful tower of macarons!\NSo delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eating sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Charlotte Linlin continued wreaking havoc{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and became a threat to the world overnight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you become\Nthe king of the sea like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I'll guarantee you a peaceful dreamland!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you all just listen to me,\NI know you'll be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:19:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those who don't listen are selfish\Nso I've got to kill them!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother, I miss you...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I miss you!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll make everyone big one day!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, let's sit around the table together again!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there are still people\Nwho don't listen to me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so sad and I can't stop crying!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because the one-and-only portrait of Mother...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're a good girl.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one-and-only portrait of Mother\Nthat was precious to me...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...got broken by them!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't forgive...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't forgive...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Straw Hats!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't forgive them!!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, since I can fly,\NI'll plunge into the site with a mirror to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once you finish,\Ndive into Caesar's mirror quickly!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unfortunately, it's time to do my job!\NDammit!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe the launchers that I made were destroyed!\NThat monster old bag! After all, she's the Emperor of the Sea!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Retreat, everyone!\NDive into the mirror!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What unbelievable wind pressure!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no! We're on the rooftop!\NWe have nowhere else to go!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.71,0:23:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have no chance of winning, either!!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others get caught by\Nthe formidable Big Mom Pirates.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's when those five finally\Nunite their strength and stand up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Germa 66, the group of modified humans that terrorized the world,\Nshows their true power!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Evil Army! Transform! Germa 66!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
